+- **HIGH** (partial-archive): `.age.complete` sidecar written only after step 5 manifest append; day-sentinel checks the sidecar (not the `.age`); failed probes rename `.age` → `.age.quarantine-<UTC>`; prune service extended.
+- **HIGH** (concurrent race): archive-wide `flock -x -w 30` at `/var/lock/iago-os-archive.lock` (fd 200) acquired before day-sentinel, held through manifest + completion write.
+
